.recipes-filter
	form.recipes-filter__form
		fieldset.recipes-filter__fieldset
			legend.recipes-filter__legend Прием пищи
			.recipes-filter__box
				input#eatingBreakfast.recipes-filter__checkbox(type='checkbox' name='eatingBreakfast')
				label.recipes-filter__label(for='eatingBreakfast') Завтрак
			.recipes-filter__box
				input#eatingLunch.recipes-filter__checkbox(type='checkbox' name='eatingLunch' checked='')
				label.recipes-filter__label(for='eatingLunch') Обед
			.recipes-filter__box
				input#eatingDinner.recipes-filter__checkbox(type='checkbox' name='eatingDinner')
				label.recipes-filter__label(for='eatingDinner') Ужин
		fieldset.recipes-filter__fieldset
			legend.recipes-filter__legend Количество ингредиентов
			.recipes-filter__inner
				.recipes-filter__box
